de.sciss.jcollider
Class Constant

java.lang.Object
  de.sciss.jcollider.Constant
All Implemented Interfaces:
Constants, GraphElem, UGenInput
public class Constant
extends Object
implements UGenInput, Constants

A Constant is a wrapper for a constant in a UGen graph. It implements the UGenInput interface and therefore also the GraphElem interface which describes heterogeneous elements of a UGen graph.

Version:
0.2, 11-Sep-05 (some countries are still at war)
